        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "Zamru l'Adonai b'chinor,\nb'chinor v'kol zimrah.\nBachatzotz'rot v'kol shofar\nhariu lifnei HaMelech Adonai.\nYiram hayam um'lo-o\nteiveil v'yoshvei vah.\nN'harot yimcha-u chaf\nyachad harim y'raneinu.\nLifnei Adonai ki va\nlishpot haaretz\nyishpot teiveil b'tzedek\nv'amim b'meisharim.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-14T17:47:13.390Z",
